at the beginning and end of each shot.

message.raw:
Added workaround for old pulseblasters which do not report their status
and as such have no way to detect end-of-run. End-of-run is now based
on a fixed duration equal to the shot duration plus some extra time
to account for waits and software delays.

This change is backward compatible.
